data.description: THIS WONDERFUL COZY HOME IS WAITING FOR YOU!! Step into a lovely living room open to the kitchen and off of that is a family room with a brick surround fireplace. So much usable and function space, yet beautiful! Step out into a fully enclosed all seasons rear porch and fenced in rear yard. Loads of possibilities! This is a 3 bedroom and the primary bedroom is an on suite. Live 25-30 minutes to Charlotte and the airport while enjoying everything this property and Charlotte has to offer.
